INCIPIT grimoire "sigilo_genus_instantiation_basic_10b"

SIGILLUM Capsa GENUS(T)
  valor: T
FIN SIGILLUM

RITUALE identitas GENUS(T)(T valor) REDDE T
  REDDE valor
EXPLICIT RITUALE

RITUALE main() REDDE REX
  EVOCA Capsa GENUS(REX) c
  VINCIRE c.valor AD CONIURA identitas GENUS(REX)(12)
  REDDE c.valor
EXPLICIT RITUALE

EXPLICIT grimoire
